00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:41.140
Patrick: The belt is just mainly the decorations, we'll put pouches on the belts and stuff like that.

00:03:41.140 --> 00:03:44.560
Yeah. Practicality for pouches is always important to me, so maybe she'll have a few pouches?

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:45.260
Patrick: Yeah.

