00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:52.760
and she just wears it around her shoulder.

00:03:52.760 --> 00:03:55.580
Patrick: The personality doesn't only come from the characters, but it comes from the weapons.

00:03:55.580 --> 00:03:59.720
And...the way they lend themselves to each other is...very unique.

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:05.760
The weapons tend to be a pretty big part of RWBY.

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:10.260
People were able to identify very early on unique aspects of some of the weapons.

00:04:10.260 --> 00:04:12.420
One of the earliest ideas I had was a

00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:18.180
giant, like, high-caliber sniper rifle with a blade attached, where it would use the kick

00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:23.320
and when firing the scythe whilst the blade is hooked on an enemy, the kick from the gun would just

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:26.800
you know, take that blade and just like (explosion noise) like pull it through an enemy.

00:04:28.220 --> 00:04:30.120
"Whoa! Is that a scythe?"

00:04:30.340 --> 00:04:32.880
"It's also a customizable,  high-impact sniper rifle."

