00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:24.360
Monty: When we had the need to have a concept artist for environments

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.860
I had one person in mind, and it was Kristina.

00:05:26.860 --> 00:05:32.440
This year you're art director because we need a lot more hands-on and the environments are looking so much better now.

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:35.080
Kristina: I work one-on-one, mostly with the modelers.

00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:38.320
It gets the job done really quick 'cause I get to see their progress

00:05:38.320 --> 00:05:43.160
and then I can do-- I can ask them to do a really quick color change. If that's not working they can change it

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:48.420
I learned a lot from just...seeing how the modelers work, too, and how they can work with me

00:05:48.420 --> 00:05:51.160
so they don't have do to, like, too many big changes.

